Business Brief -- R.R. Donnelley  Sons Co.:
   Venture Formed in London
   With Unit of G.A. Pindar
The planned venture will operate from the London
facilities of both units, Donnelley said, "with access to
printing and typesetting facilities throughout the U.K., the
U.S., continental Europe and the Far East."
   Donnelley, the largest printing concern in the U.S., has
been aggressively expanding its overseas operations in recent
years.